Package: AlzheiMarkers
Title: Analyze Metabolomic Biomarkers for Alzheimer's Disease
Version: 0.2.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Dany", "Mukesha", , 
        "danymukesha@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
        comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0001-9514-751X"))
Description: This package provides tools for analyzing metabolomic biomarkers
    to distinguish Alzheimer's Disease (AD) patients from Healthy Controls (HC).
    It includes functions for data preparation, model training, evaluation, and
    visualization of results.
